BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json1 to (do shell script "curl https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v1/ticker/kucoin-shares/")set AppleScript's text item delimiters to "["set json2 to text item 2 of json1set AppleScript's text item delimiters to "]"set json to text item 1 of json2tell application "JSON Helper"	set result to read JSON from json	set price to price_usd of resultend tellset result_string to "$" & price & ""
